				\begin{document}$$200\;\hbox {GeV}$$\end{document}). These SRs require events with no leptons and low jet multiplicity. SRt1, SRt2 and SRt3 are optimised to detect events in which DM is produced in association with a tt¯\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
