Comparison of the data with the post-fit Monte Carlo prediction of some kinematic distributions in control and validation regions. The bottom panel shows the ratio of the data to the Monte Carlo prediction. The band includes all systematic uncertainties defined in Sect. 6. The last bins include overflows, where applicable. The top left panel shows the ET,ℓℓmiss\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
